Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:23.51,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:25.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:40.02,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:41.38,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:46.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.91,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.00,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.59,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:55.37,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:43.72,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a message plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:47.42,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Its message is a warning\nto us who live today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:51.43,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,from an unknown civilization\nbuilt long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:55.52,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,that vanished into the distant\nreaches of eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:02.77,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It says, "We return our arts to the dark\nfrom which they were created. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:06.87,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,"Never to be summoned\na second time. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.91,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with this message,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:12.92,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,an organization called\nArcam was formed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:15.65,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,to seal away know ledge of\nthis ancient civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:20.74,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We know Arcam's special\noperatives as...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.82,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spriggan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.06,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:01.13,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, Red Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.20,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.80,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:16.11,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's just me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.42,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.99,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Ominae!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:17.91,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,First you miss weeks of school,\nand now you fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:18.94,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:21.55,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.28,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.58,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:32.87,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared, and his parents\ncalled the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.68,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Then yesterday, he just showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.89,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks really worn out though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.52,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.94,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Ominae...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.70,sprig alt2,,0000,0000,0000,,NOAH WILL BE YOUR GRAVE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.83,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:28.14,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:32.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.81,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.14,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:08:00.75,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yamamoto, what is\nthis Noah about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.16,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:10.46,sprig alt2,,0000,0000,0000,,You Ominae\Nyour turn come next
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:15.16,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that six months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:18.76,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,an Arcam investigation unit was wiped\nout on Mt. Ararat in Turkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.80,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've heard the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:26.29,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, they found Noah's Ark there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.01,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's Ark?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.28,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:33.91,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as it says in the legend of\nthe flood in the Old Testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:37.41,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Genesis, chapters six through nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:42.32,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,As time passed, evil came to thrive on\nthe Earth that God had created.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:46.42,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Lord repented, resolving\nto destroy mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.29,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,But He had Noah, a righteous man,\nbuild an ark,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:53.29,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,placing his family and two of every\nsort of creature upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:56.30,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that got to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.70,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:03.41,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Three weeks ago in a place\nseparate from the ark,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:06.71,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,another of our investigative\nunits was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:03.15,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,This picture was taken afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:07.06,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Three weeks ago? Why wasn't I told?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:13.67,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that it's you they're after.\NIt's too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:17.34,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yamamoto, they turned my\nfriend into a walking bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.36,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,And you want me to just stand by\nand do nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:25.25,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The Noah ruins are very\ndangerous for Arcam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:29.49,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't send you to a place like that\nin your current condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:32.59,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,This job is out of the question\nwhile you're still hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:35.38,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this time now to have\nyourself properly treated...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.23,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:40.42,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a direct challenge!\NI'll settle this myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:42.96,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.35,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.13,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:17.52,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Meisel is currently onsite,\nexamining Noah's Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.39,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps Meisel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:28.07,sprig up,,0000,0000,0000,,We are about to enter Turkish air space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:48.06,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighter of unknown nationality has\nordered a change of heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:51.37,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission to land at Diyarbakir\nhas been withdrawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.93,sprig up,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing course for Istanbul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.13,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We will contact Arcam's Turkish\noffice to have someone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:02.03,sprig up,,0000,0000,0000,,at Istanbul Airport ready with\nfurther arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:06.63,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, such hospitality!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:01.83,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You here to start a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:13.01,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Confiscated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:18.15,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:21.66,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,They were supposed to have been told.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:24.42,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's take our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:46.03,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:50.24,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,were the guys behind us told too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:53.53,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:58.36,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,They're friends of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.93,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:08.23,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,are in concrete at the bottom\nof the Bosporus Strait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.57,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who sent you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:37.28,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're not ready to take me on yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:47.45,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Spriggan, Yu Ominae,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.30,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,a member of the special\noperatives unit of Arcam,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:54.10,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,which seeks to seal off dangerous\nruins of ancient civilizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:57.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,He has rare athletic ability and reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.97,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only seventeen, but he's their\nnumber one operative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.75,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,His real abilities are nothing\ncompared to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:08.24,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Your petty tricks won't\nwork against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.73,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:15.32,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that he once\nbetrayed your unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.63,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.64,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid we've lost track of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:47.96,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He's bound to show\nup here sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:51.16,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcam's just a private army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.99,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bury him under that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:58.03,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't we, Colonel MacDougall?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.32,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:28.64,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That's got to be one of Arcam's.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:21.30,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:23.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:28.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell just opens fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.31,0:24:20.66,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,How far are we going anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.66,0:24:23.69,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Says the inept spy. Just keep\nyour mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.26,0:24:27.25,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I already told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:30.66,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcam people don't dress like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.40,0:24:33.60,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't my choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.31,0:24:46.21,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps! Doc Meisel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.68,0:24:48.88,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Margaret, you're here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.88,0:24:50.55,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you settle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.76,0:24:54.26,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NGet your hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.35,0:24:52.57,sprig alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.46,0:24:57.01,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this ruckus about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.07,0:24:59.78,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, it's me! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.78,0:25:10.97,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.38,0:25:13.69,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.38,0:25:16.57,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.65,0:25:24.33,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Ominae Yu, our\nnumber one Spriggan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.75,0:25:27.35,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! This kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.56,0:25:30.85,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.04,0:25:49.02,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, I hear they're trying to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.29,0:25:54.67,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Yamamoto in Tokyo\nwas very worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.67,0:26:01.56,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you snuck out of the hospital and\ncommandeered one of our planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.56,0:26:04.05,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.57,0:26:07.33,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.40,0:26:15.34,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The latest armored muscle suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.58,0:26:19.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It uses a metal called orihalcon\nthat reacts with the nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.96,0:26:30.55,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a battle suit of orihalcon fibers\nand artificial muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.61,0:26:32.87,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heat and pressure resistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.99,0:26:37.25,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It increases your strength\nabout thirty times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.57,0:26:49.66,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it been since\nwe had some time off?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.47,0:26:53.25,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,About two years, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.84,0:26:58.75,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an orihalcon fighting knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.75,0:27:00.76,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,With a knuckle-guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.00,0:27:15.08,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.22,0:27:19.94,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,An armguard with approximately\nfifty meters of climbing wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.94,0:27:22.32,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a powerful climbing\nclaw at the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.31,0:27:28.83,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got a high-capacity motor that\ncan lift two or three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.08,0:27:36.25,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you'd need to arm\nyourself with that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.13,0:27:50.43,sprig up,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.48,0:27:53.69,sprig up,,0000,0000,0000,,Unidentified intruders at Site 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.94,0:27:57.90,sprig up,,0000,0000,0000,,All guard units and medics\nreport at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.67,0:27:59.94,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.17,0:28:07.83,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how this stuff works.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.49,0:28:16.08,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.84,0:28:31.74,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.66,0:28:58.46,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out! Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.18,0:29:12.67,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.53,0:29:28.12,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, are you guys stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.60,0:29:31.00,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.91,0:29:38.87,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spriggan!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.68,0:29:42.67,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu Ominae!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.93,0:30:07.33,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard, you're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.87,0:30:13.36,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Fat Man, he's all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.72,0:30:21.21,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.75,0:30:29.16,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're\ngoing, traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.36,0:30:30.01,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.77,0:30:44.36,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Fat Man, you're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.16,0:31:08.96,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That was pitiful! Has joining Arcam\nslowed you down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.18,0:31:29.95,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.34,0:31:51.76,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us what you can really do,\nthe way we taught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.64,0:31:54.13,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.76,0:32:14.56,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.16,0:32:16.96,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.80,0:32:20.42,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,A Spriggan, Jean Jacquemonde.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.51,0:32:21.69,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Meisel?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.53,0:32:24.58,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick on someone your own age.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.51,0:32:33.30,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.47,0:32:44.56,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.36,0:32:49.46,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have you to thank\nfor this body of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.68,0:33:07.29,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Ominae!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.74,0:33:08.59,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.35,0:33:11.71,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.15,0:33:17.97,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to so much trouble\nto brainwash that kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.86,0:33:21.43,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is the best you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.90,0:33:31.57,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm going to wring your neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.67,0:33:32.23,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Ominae!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.23,0:33:34.11,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,...with this machine I call a body!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.67,0:33:47.38,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally shown\Nyour true face!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.60,0:34:51.06,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.72,0:35:06.70,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.89,0:35:24.43,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Boy and Fat Man have\nfailed to recapture Meisel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.92,0:35:26.92,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but big talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.92,0:35:30.92,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew this would happen.\NIt's about what we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.43,0:35:35.62,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,But Colonel, what if Arcam\ngets into the Ark?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.83,0:35:37.19,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.30,0:35:42.70,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We analyzed the magnetic field it\ndestroyed our satellite with
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.70,0:35:46.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,and the results have been quite useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.38,0:35:55.34,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The plate and stone tablet found at\neach of the ruins verifies this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.55,0:35:59.34,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We have the key to Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.12,0:36:02.35,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.29,0:36:07.43,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill anyone who interferes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.00,0:36:11.59,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,All you need do is shut up\nand follow my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.72,0:36:35.12,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You look very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.43,0:36:44.05,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.27,0:36:49.50,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,My old commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.57,0:36:56.57,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Ominae, what did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.52,0:37:05.53,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.56,0:37:11.62,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's their fault that you're\Nlike this now or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.33,0:37:14.32,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.33,0:37:19.63,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so hung up on the past\nyou forget your job now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.97,0:37:25.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,When you act like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.47,0:37:30.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,you endangered every one who's\nentrusted you with their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.96,0:37:47.66,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the information\nfrom our probe satellite,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.66,0:37:49.46,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,the magnetic fields are focusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.69,0:37:53.16,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Meisel's investigation is proceeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.37,0:37:55.77,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be getting\nclose to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.20,0:37:58.00,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.41,0:38:03.57,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is serious.\NI suggest we act.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.88,0:38:09.98,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.92,0:38:14.14,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,MacDougall will handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.56,0:38:15.92,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,But General!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.40,0:38:19.64,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being kept fully informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.93,0:38:22.73,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.73,0:38:28.23,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been indoctrinated with the\nobjectives of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.15,0:39:15.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is Noah's Ark?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.22,0:39:20.62,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bigger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.34,0:39:47.75,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Old Testament, its length\Nis 300 cubits, by a width of 50 cubits,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.75,0:39:50.51,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is at least four times that size.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.34,0:40:15.33,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The material it's made of isn't\nmere wood either.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.88,0:40:21.61,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Our current technology can't even\nscratch it, much less break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.49,0:41:02.48,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.73,0:41:08.72,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.20,0:41:15.11,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's made of some kind of\ntime-stop material.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.50,0:41:16.36,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.31,0:41:21.12,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Time doesn't flow, so you\ncan never break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.52,0:41:32.51,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,This might not have been\nmade by human hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.21,0:41:52.50,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for making the rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.74,0:42:24.93,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You're U.S. Machine Corps, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.51,0:42:27.20,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,U.S. Machine Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.88,0:42:32.37,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyborgs attached to the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.22,0:42:36.69,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.39,0:42:42.20,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be here soon. The man with\nthe power of the Devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.88,0:43:08.81,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We are in control here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.98,0:43:13.18,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay down your weapons and\ndo as I say, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.64,0:43:33.63,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.08,0:43:45.08,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.69,0:43:49.59,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.96,0:43:51.83,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.83,0:43:52.85,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.10,0:43:55.77,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.26,0:44:00.28,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, if you insist on ending up the\nsame as him, that's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.10,0:44:03.80,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.91,0:44:08.45,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.25,0:44:16.18,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tough as a cockroach\nto survive my attack wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.59,0:44:20.96,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes more than that to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.23,0:44:29.56,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,A cockroach is much better\noff on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.03,0:44:30.81,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.06,0:44:32.48,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.80,0:44:35.60,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.11,0:44:43.51,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What good will it do for\Nyou to die needlessly?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.68,0:44:48.58,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Meisel and Miss Margaret,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.58,0:44:51.62,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,we meet at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.10,0:45:07.64,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am Lord of the sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.64,0:45:12.94,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,"Awaken me, and have dominion\nover what enfolds the Earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.41,0:45:16.41,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,"When evil runs rampant on the Earth,"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.41,0:45:20.01,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,"change the blessings of Heaven\nto those of Hell"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.01,0:45:23.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,"and create humanity anew."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.22,0:45:29.37,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the message left on the\nstone tablet that we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.92,0:45:32.87,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting that together with your data,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.43,0:45:38.13,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,the "blessings of Heaven" are\nthe sun's ultra-violet rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.13,0:45:43.61,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,By adjusting the ozone layer and\ncarbon dioxide that enfold earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.61,0:45:46.60,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,you control ultra-violet radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.11,0:45:51.60,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Noah is an\natmospheric control system!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.82,0:45:54.10,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.35,0:45:57.89,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.97,0:46:07.85,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! That data\nis government property!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.00,0:46:16.41,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You will enter Noah's Ark with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.85,0:46:19.92,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't refuse
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.28,0:46:24.04,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,if you care about these people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.86,0:46:27.42,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.85,0:46:30.68,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You are disobeying orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.39,0:46:36.60,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.45,0:47:08.55,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.61,0:47:29.60,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're MacDougall?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.28,0:47:34.38,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a magnetic amplifier\nimplanted in your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.38,0:47:38.12,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know that one mistake,\nand it's brain death for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.12,0:47:41.12,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,At best, you'll live about\nfive more years.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.12,0:47:45.54,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I see why the Pentagon is so\nanxious to secure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.26,0:47:50.87,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,How many crimes have they justified\nin the name of the States!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.87,0:47:55.27,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,They conducted countless human\nexperiments to create you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.00,0:48:00.31,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the product of a government's\nmonstrous ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.31,0:48:02.88,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-fashioned sentimentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.88,0:48:06.06,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I was not chosen\nby the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.25,0:48:10.07,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It was God that chose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.36,0:48:13.05,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.81,0:48:35.22,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you now, Spriggan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.19,0:48:50.59,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.13,0:48:53.03,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.72,0:49:17.13,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.19,0:49:25.79,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Smart boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.50,0:49:31.80,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care about what\nhappens to your friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.87,0:49:34.46,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Try me and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.04,0:50:15.73,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's resonating!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.45,0:50:20.82,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you had the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.93,0:50:44.43,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Meisel, the rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.50,0:50:55.27,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower the walls! Seal off this block!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.97,0:51:23.89,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.58,0:51:39.82,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some meaning behind\nthe location of the Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.06,0:51:46.07,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would it be here at the top of\na mountain that stands alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.92,0:51:54.99,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the Ark itself is what\ncaused the flood?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.20,0:52:01.70,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps Mt. Ararat exerts a strong\nmagnetic field that suppresses it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.75,0:52:13.27,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.38,0:52:15.26,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, we're in\nuncharted territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.40,0:52:17.11,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what might happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.18,0:52:19.36,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.64,0:53:13.24,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.93,0:53:37.70,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.71,0:54:24.20,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.86,0:55:06.65,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.90,0:55:10.64,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.40,0:55:16.45,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Ominae, where's that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.69,0:55:19.60,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,They were headed towards the Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.77,0:55:22.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got old man Meisel and\nhis assistant as hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.01,0:55:26.24,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, get them first!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.71,0:55:27.41,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.41,0:55:29.06,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.86,0:55:38.11,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Ominae!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.29,0:55:43.89,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.95,0:55:48.05,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.10,0:56:10.38,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.16,0:56:14.48,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.66,0:56:16.25,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.55,0:56:25.13,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The door's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.24,0:56:27.10,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.10,0:56:29.40,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.75,0:56:31.28,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you follow them?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.49,0:56:33.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.55,0:56:35.53,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.81,0:56:42.62,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Light doesn't go in there. I 've\nnever seen anything Iike it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.81,0:57:06.61,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is Noah's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.71,0:57:12.81,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Noah's control panel!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.26,0:57:34.13,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.38,0:58:02.09,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.60,0:58:07.79,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.32,0:58:26.31,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.40,0:59:14.30,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the seal is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.46,0:59:15.41,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.04,0:59:51.94,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.77,1:00:03.58,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.85,1:00:06.69,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, while arms reductions are\Nprogressing over the world...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.69,1:00:09.91,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,the environment is considered\nto be the biggest problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.10,1:00:14.67,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Acid rain, ozone depletion,\nglobal warming...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.67,1:00:18.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,With Noah we can solve\nall these problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.52,1:00:33.10,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,MacDougall, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.45,1:00:37.65,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,If the atomic bomb is the\nsymbol of power,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.65,1:00:39.61,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,then Noah will surely become\nthe symbol of peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.71,1:00:43.79,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,My country must be the world's\nleader at all times, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.79,1:00:47.36,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,And to do that, we absolutely had\nto get our hands on this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.19,1:00:53.36,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does the Pentagon want it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.47,1:00:58.13,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Using it would be like signing your\nown country's death warrant.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.90,1:01:06.08,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.16,1:01:27.11,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dead?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.44,1:01:31.77,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.81,1:01:43.05,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah probably caused the ice age\nthat destroyed the dinosaurs,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.05,1:01:47.34,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,but it has other functions besides\nchanging the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.76,1:01:52.89,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a crazy theory that no\none would believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.86,1:01:57.53,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,But seeing those dinosaurs\nconvinced me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.53,1:02:02.04,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The dinosaurs and all those\nother strange creatures
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.04,1:02:05.88,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,must be there for experiments
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.88,1:02:09.31,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,to create the next generation\nof new animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.32,1:02:20.17,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.52,1:02:24.69,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Noah is also a machine\nfor the generation of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.03,1:02:30.60,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Doctor? Isn't it splendid?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.69,1:02:34.56,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Human history started right\nhere in Noah's Ark!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.03,1:02:39.40,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, let us create a whole new\nworld with our very hands!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.27,1:02:44.71,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! So, that's what\nyou wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.02,1:02:47.92,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Mankind took the wrong\npath down history.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.92,1:02:51.25,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Mankind is God's one and\nonly creative failure!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.28,1:02:55.49,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So you intend to take God's place and\npass judgment on mankind?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.49,1:02:57.12,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.15,1:03:01.17,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to use Noah to create the\nnext generation of life forms.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.21,1:03:04.88,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.39,1:03:08.38,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, work with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.97,1:03:09.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.31,1:03:17.10,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Where the hell are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.42,1:03:25.08,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.40,1:03:29.28,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, no! You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.62,1:03:36.02,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.51,1:03:52.51,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.92,1:04:21.19,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring a fire extinguisher!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.27,1:04:21.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.48,1:04:29.12,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.96,1:04:37.45,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.06,1:04:40.01,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.97,1:04:44.06,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ark's moving!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.60,1:04:49.63,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this shaking?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.18,1:05:00.66,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn kid's moving the Ark!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.92,1:05:06.65,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I've started the warming mode.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.86,1:05:09.36,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The polar ice caps will melt
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.36,1:05:12.36,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,and the warmer water will cause\nabnormalities in the weather.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.36,1:05:14.76,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The majority of the land will be flooded.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.93,1:05:18.59,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what will you do, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.17,1:05:21.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no going back.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.98,1:06:03.28,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the start of the second flood legend!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.56,1:06:19.55,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That cockroach! So he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.94,1:06:28.17,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,If it can't be broken from outside,\NI'll do it from within!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.42,1:06:45.22,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot down this ship\nalong with that brat!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.39,1:06:49.88,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.84,1:07:00.11,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.14,1:07:04.63,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.78,1:07:15.65,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.65,1:07:17.22,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.22,1:07:18.71,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.06,1:07:29.03,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.27,1:07:34.26,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the Doc, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.77,1:07:40.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu! We have to seal Noah off!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.45,1:07:46.91,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Get him out!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.55,1:07:49.62,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The plate...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.81,1:07:51.61,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.27,1:08:10.50,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I gave him the chance\nto work with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.04,1:08:14.39,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your man now!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.64,1:08:18.31,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you with me down\nto the bottom of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.68,1:08:24.18,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of fool enters a holy\nplace with his boots on?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.39,1:08:26.82,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit playing with fire like a kid already!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.63,1:08:32.66,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to want to take me\nto the grave with you,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.93,1:08:35.99,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll have to go to\NHell by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.40,1:08:40.53,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Very funny. And a kid like you is\ngoing to send me there?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.08,1:08:55.79,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.79,1:08:59.98,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Your orihalcon suit that you're so\nproud of is like a toy to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.53,1:09:07.73,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stop defiling the House\nof God with your blood?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.60,1:09:10.58,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,House of God?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.63,1:09:13.43,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What god is there here?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.94,1:09:17.24,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,God is Noah and the one who uses it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.12,1:09:21.34,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you call this mass\nmurdering device a god?!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.28,1:09:24.78,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as it has been in\nancient times past,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.78,1:09:28.08,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,the power of Noah is given only\nto those who are chosen.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.49,1:09:31.89,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Scum like you have no right to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.19,1:09:34.97,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just being used!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.09,1:09:39.99,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand that for them\nyou're just an expendable item?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.63,1:09:49.04,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither the Pentagon nor the\NMachine Corps concern me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.11,1:09:56.41,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,With these hands, I will judge\ntheir rotten hearts.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.75,1:09:59.04,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Get serious!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.32,1:10:00.81,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.05,1:10:32.54,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.41,1:11:01.00,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead, finally.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.59,1:11:12.18,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Project Cosmos...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.36,1:11:19.23,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Pentagon's special experimental unit
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.23,1:11:21.87,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,that raised children to\nbecome elite killers.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.43,1:11:27.53,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's where you come from,\NNumber 43.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.00,1:12:05.50,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not a number.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.08,1:12:13.68,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Yu Ominae.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.24,1:12:42.47,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the story. You wiped out\nthe entire unit all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.54,1:13:43.84,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Number 43!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.81,1:13:47.71,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop your gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.51,1:13:51.44,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.52,1:13:55.44,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, 43?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.62,1:13:56.65,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.75,1:13:59.07,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu Ominae!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.96,1:14:06.16,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a killing machine too.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.23,1:14:08.82,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.00,1:14:45.83,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw your parents' death\nin the people you killed?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.40,1:14:49.30,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all it took to drive you mad?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.54,1:14:52.78,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.78,1:14:55.09,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I am human.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.28,1:15:01.88,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die before I become
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.19,1:15:12.32,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,an instrument for killing again!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.70,1:15:14.73,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Human, you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.90,1:15:20.57,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You think a mere human can strike\nme down?! I am God!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.25,1:15:35.52,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.52,1:15:39.46,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a god is man-made?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.77,1:15:44.97,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah is starting to go out of control\nin response to your powers!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.61,1:15:50.70,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you can do\nwith that body made of junk?!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.53,1:15:57.74,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I am God! I will destroy\nthe human race!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.47,1:16:03.85,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.68,1:16:06.41,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You die!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.70,1:16:57.25,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.29,1:17:31.17,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Just when the nightmare\nwas about to wash away.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.88,1:17:43.14,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wild fantasy is over, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.15,1:17:50.89,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.06,1:17:55.06,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm not an instrument for killing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.47,1:18:12.70,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah is now in destruct mode.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.01,1:18:13.91,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.68,1:18:18.08,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The inside of the Ark was an alternate\ndimensional space,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.08,1:18:21.05,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,but now, it'll be swallowed up\nby our third dimension!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.92,1:18:23.41,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.76,1:18:29.96,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found many other magnetic\nfields like Noah's.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.96,1:18:32.70,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It means there are lots of other\nruins with powers like this
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.70,1:18:35.39,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,all over the world, just\nwaiting to be found!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.70,1:18:43.97,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The real fight has only just\nbegun, Spriggan!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.66,1:19:07.22,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.97,1:19:16.56,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The Ark!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.36,1:19:44.66,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I'm not gonna make it...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.87,1:19:53.54,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Ominae!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.68,1:19:59.14,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, this is no place to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.51,1:20:01.75,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.98,1:20:02.94,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.37,1:20:06.52,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I am too soft.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.82,1:20:10.31,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still see that kid's\nface in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.69,1:20:12.65,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's soft,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.33,1:20:17.13,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's what I like about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.10,1:20:19.74,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.74,1:20:22.23,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and let me carry you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.73,1:20:51.19,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.44,1:21:03.54,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's what the Ark really looks like.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.57,1:21:26.39,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crumbling!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.47,1:21:29.27,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! We couldn't even scratch it!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.31,1:21:35.71,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,4,000 years have suddenly returned!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.63,1:22:31.03,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ark is destroyed. All has\nreturned to nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.20,1:22:34.53,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Yu and Jean?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.27,1:23:12.72,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.19,1:23:26.68,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.69,1:23:29.28,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.56,1:23:35.05,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.23,0:50:46.23,sprig,,0000,0000,0000,,
